    "description": "VIT University South Asia Partners has an exciting opening for a Senior Teacher at our Gurgaon office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout VIT University South Asia Partners:\nVIT University South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with VIT University South Asia Partners!",
